{"tid":677966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容海恩言論辣㷫外傭組織 周日發起遊行到新民黨總部抗議","createTime":"2018-05-25T15:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T16:05:39.000Z","uid":29675,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f672b3815e2c21e03a126e70f3a2df46b164de21","tid":677966,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"新民黨立法會議員容海恩前日在立法會大會上，投訴外傭在假日時聚集影響市民生活和環境衛生，促請勞工及福利局局長羅致光想辦法紓緩問題。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲移居人士聯盟對容海恩的言論感憤怒，發言人Eman直指對方「無知」，反問香港有逾38萬名來港工作的外傭，質疑他們在假日時間一下子可到那兒休息。<br />\n<br />\nEman認為外傭假日在中環、銅鑼灣等席地而坐，相信市民都理解，亦已成為港人生活一部分。聯盟本周日將發起抗議活動，由中環遊行至新民黨位於灣仔的總部，要求容海恩就言論道歉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f540c1d33521b8a6daf959a3ba3758a06c64d1","tid":677966,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a5415cd7a8efabd86586eb51ea94842e7c8337","tid":677966,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"強烈要求新民黨開放各地辦俾外傭姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b8de32cc3d1fbf63bd21052edbb775fe779074","tid":677966,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"655b8fb4fb79f119289f64c3c64f96951e6c0ec0","tid":677966,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"200a4760455d384781b04bb9284850c2eb5eb618","tid":677966,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a5415cd7a8efabd86586eb51ea94842e7c8337","tid":677966,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"強烈要求新民黨開放各地辦俾外傭姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=